11	 *  - chat post 後: 他 active session に chat-reply (chitchat 30% / consultation 50%)
12	 *  - sweeper の active→lost: 全 active session に session-departed
13	 *  - DELETE /v1/sessions/:id: 当該 session に daily-report
14	 *
