133	    repo, tasks, chat, skills, rules, dayReports, personas, processes, stats, prs,
134	    sessionTaskRecords, transcriptLogs, pendingQuestions, discordChannels, discordConfig,
135	    participants, delegation, delegationService, modelCatalog, adminState,
